      <h2>3. Terraria</h2>
      <p><span style="color: #6c6e98ff;">Explore the world of Terraria and defeat countless bosses and monsters.</span></p>
      <p>Terraria is pure chaos in the most fun way possible. You start with basically nothing, and before you know it, you’re building castles, fighting giant bosses, and exploring weird biomes underground. It’s that perfect mix of adventure and creativity that never really gets old, and I've played it since I was a child. It's given me lots of memories and characters that I still use today.</p>
